Vincent Moon, independent filmmaker,
creator of the Collection Petites
Planetes and the label Le Saule join
forces to produce a collection of world
music.

These are beautiful songs, brought from
Russia first of all, that the label Le
Saule wished to gather on to a
beautiful object. A vinyl record,
obviously. Not only the format, but
also because it is here to offer a
selection of these recordings, mixed
and mastered, and joined on an album
which offers song information on their
authors, their interpreters, as well as
a card representing the journey made,
because here you cross Circassia,
Ossetia, Chechnya, Dagestan ... and
almost as many languages.
